The '''Red Knights of Life''' were fanatical followers of [[Nom Anor]] on [[Rhommamool/Legends|Rhommamool]] who enforced the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]'s [[Anti-droid sentiment/Legends|hatred]] of mechanical technology. They were secretly being manipulated by the Yuuzhan Vong.<ref name="TCSWE">''[[The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia]]''</ref>

The Knights were formed by Anor sometime between [[11 ABY/Legends|11 ABY]], after his killing of the [[Imperial Ruling Council/Legends#The "Council of Blood"|Imperial Interim Ruling Council]], and [[13 ABY/Legends|13 ABY]], at which point [[Xbrr-Zinngogg]] journeyed to [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] to complain about Anor to the [[New Republic Ruling Council]]. [[Chief of State (New Republic)/Legends|Chief of State]] [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]] refused to intervene, considering it a local matter.<ref name="EL1">[[Crimson Empire III: Empire Lost 1|''Crimson Empire III: Empire Lost'' 1]]</ref>

The Knights were also strongly opposed to [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] and [[Sith/Legends|Sith]] alike, and were known to have fought on [[Osarian]] and [[Uffel]]. They rode [[tutakan]]s, fought with [[pummelstave]]s, and wore [[Color/Legends|black]] [[Cape/Legends|capes]] and red-dyed animal hides.

